\c 8
\s Udumo lweN\nd kosi\nd* lodumo lomuntu
\d Kumqondisi wokuhlabelela. NgeGithithi. Isihlabelelo sikaDavida
\p
\v 1 N\nd kosi\nd*, Nkosi yethu, lilenkazimulo kangakanani ibizo lakho emhlabeni wonke\x + Hlab. 148.13. Isa. 12.4.\x*! Omise ubukhosi bakho ngaphezu kwamazulu\x + Hlab. 113.4.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Emlonyeni wezingane lowabamunyayo umisile amandla ngenxa yezitha zakho\x + Mat. 21.16. Mat. 11.25.\x*, ukuze uthulise isitha lomphindiseli\x + Hlab. 44.16.\x*.
\v 3 Lapho ngikhangela amazulu akho, umsebenzi weminwe yakho, inyanga lenkanyezi owazimisayo\x + Eks. 8.19.\x*,
\v 4 uyini umuntu ukuthi umkhumbule\x + Heb. 2.6-8. Jobe 7.17.\x*, lendodana yomuntu ukuthi uyihambele\x + Hlab. 80.17.\x*?
\v 5 Kanti wamenza waba ngaphansi kancinyane kulengilosi, wamethwesa umqhele wobukhosi\x + Hlab. 21.5.\x* lodumo\x + Hlab. 21.5.\x*.
\v 6 Wamenza wabusa phezu kwemisebenzi yezandla zakho\x + Gen. 1.26,28.\x*, konke wakubeka ngaphansi kwenyawo zakhe\x + 1 Kor. 15.27. Mat. 28.18.\x*,
\v 7 izimvu lenkabi zonke, kanye lezinyamazana zeganga,
\v 8 inyoni zamazulu, lezinhlanzi zolwandle, okudlula ezindleleni zenlwandle\x + Gen. 1.26,28.\x*.
\p
\v 9 N\nd kosi\nd*, Nkosi yethu, lilenkazimulo kangakani ibizo lakho emhlabeni wonke\x + 8.1.\x*!